rida-3-larnaca-cyprus|title=Irida 3, Larnaca {{!}} 1273498 {{!}} EMPORIS|website=www.emporis.com|access-date=2020-01-28}}</ref></small>\n|-\n|'''16*'''\n|'''KEMA'''||[[Nicosia]]|| \u224852m\n| \u2248171ft || 12 || 1978\n|Commercial||<small>Tallest building in [[Cyprus]] from 1978 to 1996</small>\n|-\n|'''17*'''\n|[[Shacolas Tower|'''Shacolas Tower''']]||[[Nicosia]]|| 50m\n|164ft|| 11 || 1959\n|Observatory/ Commercial||<small>Tallest building in [[Cyprus]] from 1959 to 1978</small>\n|}\n== Cities with \u226550m-tall buildings ==\nList measures buildings by roof height only.\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n!City\n!\u226550m\n|-\n|[[Limassol]]\n|7\n|-\n|[[Nicosia]]\n|8\n|-\n|[[Larnaca]]\n|3\n|}\n== Buildings under construction ==\nThis lists building that are under construction or that have been proposed in Cyprus and are planned to rise at least 50 metres.\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center; width:57.5%\"\n|+<u>Status</u>:\n|-\n| width=\"60\" bgcolor=\"FFB347\" | '''Under Construction'''\n| width=\"60\" bgcolor=\"87CEFA\" | '''Approved'''\n| width=\"60\" bgcolor=\" pink\" | '''Proposed'''\n|}\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"text-align: center;\"\t\n|- style=\"text-align: center; color: navy;\"\n!<big>Rank</big>\n!                <big>Building</big>                                       \n!     <big>City</big>  \n! colspan=\"2\" |         <big>Height</big>       \n!<big>Floors</big>\n!<big>Year</big>\n!         <big>Status</big>            \n!<big>Use</big>\n!                <big>Updates</big>\n|-\n|- style=\"background :#87CEFA;\"\n|1\n|[http://www.lemesosblog.com/images/images-2/cache_876x3000_Analog_medium_186416_140305_2452018.JPG '''Aura''']\n|[[Limassol]]\n|178,5m\n|585,5ft\n|43\n|2023\n|Approved\n|Residential\n|<small>To be erected at a plot where a shopping mall currently stands<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://auralimassol.com/|title=Aura Limassol|last=|first=|date=|website=|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=}}</ref></small>\n|-